<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(في أن ولن)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(قوله)</span> : " فالناصب <span class="c2">(أن)</span> و <span class="c2">(لن)</span> .<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>